@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Server Cloud and Application Resources";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Server Cloud and Application Resources</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        Master the world of server cloud and application management with these comprehensive resources. Whether you're an aspiring IT professional or looking to refine your cloud skills, these materials provide you with hands-on guidance, industry-standard certifications, and in-depth tutorials. Learn to deploy scalable applications, manage cloud services efficiently, and develop expertise in cutting-edge cloud technologies.
    </p>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">AWS Certified Solutions Architect</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This highly regarded certification by Amazon Web Services equips you with the knowledge and skills to design, deploy, and operate highly available, cost-effective, and secure applications on AWS. It includes detailed learning paths, exam prep, and practical exercises tailored for real-world cloud solutions.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-solutions-architect-associate/" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Microsoft Azure Fundamentals</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Ideal for beginners, this certification offers a thorough introduction to Microsoft Azure services. You'll learn cloud concepts, core Azure services, pricing, and security fundamentals, making it a perfect starting point for building expertise in Azure cloud environments.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/certifications/azure-fundamentals/" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Introduction to Kubernetes</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This resource from Kubernetes.io introduces you to container orchestration, helping you manage and deploy containers across clusters effectively. It includes hands-on labs, detailed tutorials, and practical applications to get you comfortable with Kubernetes in a real-world setting.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://kubernetes.io/docs/tutorials/" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Google Cloud Fundamentals</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Learn the basics of Google Cloud Platform through interactive lessons and hands-on labs. This course covers cloud computing fundamentals, managing virtual machines, and leveraging Google Cloud's unique features to deploy scalable and efficient solutions.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://cloud.google.com/training" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">IBM Cloud Learn Hub</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        The IBM Cloud Learn Hub is your one-stop destination for cloud-native solutions. It offers resources on app modernization, AI integration, Kubernetes, and hybrid cloud setups. Perfect for those looking to explore enterprise-grade cloud tools and frameworks.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://www.ibm.com/cloud/learn" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Cloud Academy</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Cloud Academy offers a blend of interactive quizzes, hands-on labs, and comprehensive courses to help you become a cloud expert. Topics range from AWS and Azure to Google Cloud and Kubernetes, making it an excellent resource for continuous learning and certification prep.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://cloudacademy.com" class="link-resource">Open Resource</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
